From 283d69ca70f3fb894e839ae9874d434d1d7a8ae8 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Uraj Sasan <usasan@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Sun, 29 Jun 2025 20:40:16 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] wifi: ath12k: Add INI framework support in driver

Add infrastructure to parse INI files with support for multiple data types.
Introduce basic infrastructure for driver to parse INI files supporting
UINT, INT, STRING, BOOL, and MAC address types and implement dedicated
handlers for each data type.

Generate driver metadata at compile time with attributes such as name, min,
max, and handler type to guide parsing logic. Add helper APIs to initialize
and deinitialize parsing context. Include functions to print INI data
and driver metadata.Implement global and section-based parsing logic to
support structured configuration parsing.

Signed-off-by: Uraj Sasan <usasan@qti.qualcomm.com>
